it.polimi.ingsw.server.view

Class View

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.ingsw.server.view.View
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Interviewer
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RMIView, SocketView

    public abstract class View
extends java.lang.Object
implements Interviewer
    This class is an abstract server-side SocketView. It contains all the methods needed for the interaction with the controller and implements all the listeners needed to receive information from the model
